{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "Madame la Commissaire,", "start": 0.016, "duration": 0.884}, {"text": "Madame la Pr\u00e9sidente,", "start": 0.9, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "je voudrais m'associer", "start": 2.4, "duration": 0.766}, {"text": "aux remerciements de mon coll\u00e8gue Sven Simon,", "start": 3.166, "duration": 1.65}, {"text": "et \u00e0 ceux de tous mes coll\u00e8gues", "start": 4.816, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "pour vous dire", "start": 6.116, "duration": 0.417}, {"text": "que nous sommes tr\u00e8s reconnaissants", "start": 6.533, "duration": 2.133}, {"text": "que vous soyez rest\u00e9e si tard,", "start": 8.666, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "malgr\u00e9 les difficult\u00e9s de la journ\u00e9e", "start": 10.166, "duration": 1.284}, {"text": "au sein du Parlement europ\u00e9en,", "start": 11.45, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "pour cette discussion importante.", "start": 12.5, "duration": 1.566}, {"text": "Vous avez cit\u00e9 Thomas Jefferson", "start": 14.066, "duration": 2.15}, {"text": "qui disait que", "start": 16.216, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "\u201cle prix de la libert\u00e9, c'est une vigilance \u00e9ternelle\u201d, ", "start": 17.416, "duration": 2.884}, {"text": "vigilance qu'il faut garantir envers les dangers", "start": 20.3, "duration": 1.766}, {"text": "qui ne sont pas d\u00e9j\u00e0 pass\u00e9s,", "start": 22.066, "duration": 1.45}, {"text": "mais ceux qui sont devant nous.", "start": 23.516, "duration": 1.55}, {"text": "Et l'un d'entre eux, je crois,", "start": 25.066, "duration": 1.384}, {"text": "c'est celui auquel nous expose", "start": 26.45, "duration": 1.266}, {"text": "les cons\u00e9quences de l'insouciance", "start": 27.716, "duration": 1.35}, {"text": "de long terme", "start": 29.066, "duration": 0.984}, {"text": "de beaucoup d'\u00c9tats membres", "start": 30.05, "duration": 0.85}, {"text": "de l'Union europ\u00e9enne,", "start": 30.9, "duration": 1.283}, {"text": "qui ont v\u00e9cu pendant longtemps", "start": 32.183, "duration": 1.433}, {"text": "dans un monde presque fictif.", "start": 33.616, "duration": 1.867}, {"text": "Whatever it takes.", "start": 35.483, "duration": 0.983}, {"text": "Quoi qu'il en co\u00fbte.", "start": 36.466, "duration": 0.734}, {"text": "Ces mots bien connus de l'un de vos pr\u00e9d\u00e9cesseurs", "start": 37.2, "duration": 3.083}, {"text": "ont repr\u00e9sent\u00e9 une sorte d'autorisation", "start": 40.283, "duration": 2.317}, {"text": "de faire face \u00e0 toutes les crises,", "start": 42.8, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "avec la m\u00eame maxime :", "start": 44.033, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "quoi qu'il en co\u00fbte.", "start": 45.3, "duration": 1.516}, {"text": "C'\u00e9tait le Covid,", "start": 46.816, "duration": 1.45}, {"text": "aujourd'hui, c'est la hausse des prix de l'\u00e9nergie,", "start": 48.266, "duration": 2.667}, {"text": "qui fait que les dettes publiques", "start": 50.933, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "n'ont cess\u00e9 d'augmenter", "start": 52.016, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "dans beaucoup de nos pays.", "start": 52.916, "duration": 1.434}, {"text": "Or, nous le voyons,", "start": 54.35, "duration": 0.866}, {"text": "l'inflation, dont vous avez dit", "start": 55.216, "duration": 1.234}, {"text": "\u00e0 quel point elle est pesante", "start": 56.45, "duration": 1.35}, {"text": "et \u00e9prouvante", "start": 57.8, "duration": 1.016}, {"text": "pour beaucoup de m\u00e9nages europ\u00e9ens,", "start": 58.816, "duration": 2.084}, {"text": "oblige la Banque centrale europ\u00e9enne", "start": 60.9, "duration": 1.883}, {"text": "\u00e0 remonter ses taux d'int\u00e9r\u00eat.", "start": 62.783, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "Pour un pays comme le mien,", "start": 63.95, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "la France,", "start": 65.033, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "- un pays comme le n\u00f4tre, Madame la pr\u00e9sidente,", "start": 65.783, "duration": 2.883}, {"text": "chaque point d'augmentation", "start": 68.666, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "des taux d'int\u00e9r\u00eat repr\u00e9sente", "start": 69.716, "duration": 2.25}, {"text": "\u00e0 moyen terme, sur cinq ans,", "start": 71.966, "duration": 1.884}, {"text": "20 milliards\u00a0d'euros", "start": 73.85, "duration": 0.45}, {"text": "de d\u00e9penses suppl\u00e9mentaires ;", "start": 74.3, "duration": 1.416}, {"text": "Sur dix ans, 40 milliards\u00a0d'euros.", "start": 75.716, "duration": 1.65}, {"text": "Chaque point d'augmentation !", "start": 77.366, "duration": 1.534}, {"text": "Et vous l'avez dit, malheureusement,", "start": 78.9, "duration": 1.433}, {"text": "cela pourrait ne pas suffire", "start": 80.333, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "\u00e0 faire baisser l'inflation.", "start": 81.833, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "Nous risquons de nous trouver", "start": 83.25, "duration": 1.166}, {"text": "dans une situation terrible,", "start": 84.416, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "o\u00f9 nos \u00c9tats n'auraient plus les moyens", "start": 85.166, "duration": 1.317}, {"text": "d'intervenir sur le plan social", "start": 86.483, "duration": 1.467}, {"text": "en \u00e9tant confront\u00e9s \u00e0 cette asphyxie", "start": 87.95, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "que cr\u00e9erait une nouvelle crise de la dette.", "start": 90.05, "duration": 1.766}, {"text": "Alors,", "start": 91.816, "duration": 0.5}, {"text": "Madame la Pr\u00e9sidente,", "start": 92.75, "duration": 1.016}, {"text": "je n'ai qu'une seule question", "start": 93.766, "duration": 1.234}, {"text": "\u00e0 vous poser :", "start": 95.0, "duration": 0.383}, {"text": "craignez vous,", "start": 95.383, "duration": 0.667}, {"text": "vous aussi,", "start": 96.05, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "une nouvelle crise de la dette ?", "start": 96.8, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "Et ne croyez vous pas", "start": 97.85, "duration": 1.016}, {"text": "qu'il est temps de revenir", "start": 98.866, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "\u00e0 cette autre maxime", "start": 99.766, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "bien connue de Thomas Jefferson : ", "start": 100.733, "duration": 1.017}, {"text": "\u201cNe d\u00e9pensez pas votre argent", "start": 101.75, "duration": 2.35}, {"text": "avant de l'avoir gagn\u00e9\u201d.", "start": 104.1, "duration": 1.216}, {"text": "Merci beaucoup.", "start": 105.316, "duration": 2.517}]}